\": 108}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thorpe, for one, became the first Native athlete to take home two gold medals for the U.S. back in 1912, when he won the pentathlon and decathlon in Stockholm; in 1964, Mills won the gold medal in the 10,000-meter run category in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 361, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 125, \"end\": 131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thorpe\", \"score\": 0.9999222327514465, \"rank\": 7.684929879159526e-05, \"text\": \"Thorpe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thorpe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thorpe\"}, {\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stockholm\", \"score\": 0.999999987312549, \"rank\": 1.1713593761849665e-08, \"text\": \"Stockholm\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stockholm\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stockholm\"}, {\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9988010940427933, \"rank\": 0.001035965428872959, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first Native athlete\", \"from\": 149, \"to\": 173}, {\"ngram\": \"two gold medals\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 202}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 215}, {\"ngram\": \"the pentathlon\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 256}, {\"ngram\": \"decathlon\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"Mills\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 318}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10,000-meter run category\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These unsung athletes may not be household names on a global scale, but in Indian Country, they are bonafide legends.\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These unsung athletes\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"household names\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"a global scale\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"Indian Country\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"bonafide legends\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And today, a new streetwear drop is now aiming to spotlight these names through style.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new streetwear drop\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"these names\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"style\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Out now,The NTVS-an Indigenous-owned streetwear brand-has released a special Olympics capsule collection that pays homage to various Native athletes.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The NTVS\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"an Indigenous-owned streetwear brand\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"a special Olympics capsule collection\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"homage\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"various Native athletes\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the 2024 Olympic Games currently underway in Paris, owner and designer Aaron Silva says he had the idea to uplift athletes from his own community.\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 768, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999434217004, \"rank\": 5.657830128326694e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 794, \"end\": 799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Neville\", \"score\": 0.5711923713686007, \"rank\": 0.5368620857933615, \"text\": \"Aaron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Neville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Neville\"}, {\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stunt_Silva\", \"score\": 0.9959577092417891, \"rank\": 0.004058695072719515, \"text\": \"Silva\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stunt_Silva\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stunt_Silva\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"owner\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"designer\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"his own community\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It struck me that fan-wear for these incredible athletes is almost nonexistent,\\\" says founder Aaron Silva.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 965, \"end\": 970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Neville\", \"score\": 0.5711923713686007, \"rank\": 0.5368620857933615, \"text\": \"Aaron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Neville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Neville\"}, {\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stunt_Silva\", \"score\": 0.9959577092417891, \"rank\": 0.004058695072719515, \"text\": \"Silva\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stunt_Silva\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stunt_Silva\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fan-wear\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"these incredible athletes\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought it would be amazing to provide people with the opportunity to wear replications of the pieces they once wore.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"replications\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"the pieces\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This collection not only commemorates their legacy, but also supports their ongoing impact.\\\"\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This collection\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"their legacy\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"their ongoing impact\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The collection includes hats, sweatshirts, tees, tanks, and socks-all of which feature the names and numbers of Native Olympians.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The collection\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"hats\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"sweatshirts\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"tees\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"tanks\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"socks\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"the names\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"numbers\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"Native Olympians\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Prices range from $20 to $100).\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Prices\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Theunisex tank, for example, features the number 222, mirroring Mills's original running number.\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Theunisex tank\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"Mills's original running number\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Tewanima\\\" tee also features an image of the athlete running in the 1912 Olympics, when he won the silver medal; the design was created in collaboration with the Hopi artist Duane Koyawena.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hopi\", \"score\": 0.9999999998219664, \"rank\": 1.7543582360347855e-10, \"text\": \"Hopi\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hopi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hopi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The \\\"Tewanima\\\" tee\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"an image\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1912 Olympics\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver medal\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"the design\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"collaboration\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"Duane Koyawena\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even better, the collection also has a charitable component.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the collection\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"a charitable component\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A portion of all of the proceeds will be donated to the Thorpe family, as well as theBilly Mills Running Strong Foundation, which helps Indigenous youth achieve their goals and dreams.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1765, \"end\": 1771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thorpe\", \"score\": 0.9999222327514465, \"rank\": 7.684929879159526e-05, \"text\": \"Thorpe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thorpe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thorpe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A portion\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"the proceeds\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"theBilly Mills\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"Strong Foundation\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1831}, {\"ngram\": \"Indigenous youth\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"their goals\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"dreams\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Silva, it nods back to the original intent of the drop, which was to champion Native excellence.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stunt_Silva\", \"score\": 0.9959577092417891, \"rank\": 0.004058695072719515, \"text\": \"Silva\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stunt_Silva\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stunt_Silva\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the original intent\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"the drop\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"Native excellence\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love Native history, and being able to share some of their stories through fashion design is very fulfilling,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Native history\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"their stories\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"fashion design\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92025Cond\\u00e9 Nast.\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a92025Cond\\u00e9 Nast\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.Voguemay earn a portion of sales from products that are purchased through our site as part of our Affiliate Partnerships with retailers.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2296, \"entiti